        {SPEAKER NAME_S}{CREATE MUGSHOT_S EMOTE_NORMAL}.......\p
        {SPEAKER NAME_M}{CREATE MUGSHOT_M EMOTE_NORMAL}Ahem, may I ask you something?\p
        {SPEAKER NAME_S}{CREATE MUGSHOT_S EMOTE_NORMAL}Didn't you want to talk? So just fire away.\p
        {SPEAKER NAME_M}{CREATE MUGSHOT_M EMOTE_NORMAL}How did you learn to battle when you didn't have a Pokémon before?\p
        {SPEAKER NAME_S}{CREATE MUGSHOT_S EMOTE_NORMAL}They taught us in the orphanage.\p
        It'd be hard to manage if the kids have their own Pokémon so the staff lent us theirs for Pokémon battling classes.\p
        We also get a certified trainer card after graduating.\p
        {SPEAKER NAME_M}{CREATE MUGSHOT_M EMOTE_NORMAL}So that was how it worked there.\p
        {SPEAKER NAME_S}{CREATE MUGSHOT_S EMOTE_NORMAL}Anything else?\p
        {SPEAKER NAME_M}{CREATE MUGSHOT_M EMOTE_SMILE}For now, no. Thank you, that was quite informative.\p
        What about you? I figure it'll only be fair if you ask me something in return.\p
        {SPEAKER NAME_S}{CREATE MUGSHOT_S EMOTE_NORMAL}........\p
        {SPEAKER NAME_S}{CREATE MUGSHOT_S EMOTE_PENSIVE}What's your Pokémon's favorite foods...?\p
        {SPEAKER NAME_M}{CREATE MUGSHOT_M EMOTE_SURPRISED}My Pokémon's favorite foods...?\p
        {SPEAKER NAME_S}{CREATE MUGSHOT_S EMOTE_GEEZ}N-Never mind that. We're done here.\p
        {SPEAKER NAME_M}{CREATE MUGSHOT_M EMOTE_SURPRISED}Aragaki-kun?"))
        closemessage
        setvar(VAR_TEMP_2, 1)
        specialvar(VAR_RESULT, GetPlayerFacingDirection)
        if (var(VAR_RESULT) == DIR_NORTH){
            applymovement(OBJ_EVENT_ID_NPC_FOLLOWER, walkdown)
